text: @sapientxai it was awesome meeting you at Keiretsu Forum SF and hearing about your innovative ideas on monitoring vehicles needs as well as offering drivers a safer way to get things done while on the road! We hope to meet again, soon! Cheers, Your Friends at @CertentInc
Exciting news!!

Thank you to all of the investors who invested in SapientX over the past two months via SeedInvest. Thanks to you, we made our short term funding goal and we are busy making SapientX better than ever!

SapientX has been selected as one of the 18 featured startups at the Keiretsu Forum sponsored Angel Capital Expo (shark tank) on November 15th, 7:30 - 5. Information can be found at https://www. angelcapitalexpo.com / . Over 400 sharks are expected to converge at 465 California St., SF, CA.
Thanks so much!
